00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.420
&gt;&gt; When you're working with hot steel,

00:06:27.420 --> 00:06:29.880
you wanna grab the metal 
with a bare hand

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:33.970
because if you're wearing a glove,
or a plastic glove or something,

00:06:33.970 --> 00:06:38.370
